name: Flower bookmark
description:
Gorgeous bookmark with a pretty flower pattern and dangling vintage beads.

Perfect for making your books that bit more glamorous!

name: GREEN JEWEL BOOKMARK
description:
Lovely bookmark created from a vintage earring to give a glamorous look to your reading.

It's an antique gold colour with sparkling green jewels.

name: TURQUOISE BOOKMARK
description:
Pretty bookmark to make your reading even more luxurious!

It's been created from a vintage earring to make it completely unique.

Bookmark is a vintage gold colour and has a scroll pattern on it.

name: ALL THE LADS tiepin
description:
Perfect for your Best Man, an Usher, or even for the Groom.

All of our tiepins are made from the pages of old books of Scottish Fairy Tales, making each one unique.

Tiepin is silver plated.

name: FRIEND HEART NECKLACE
description:
Beautiful heart shaped sterling silver necklace stamped with the word FRIEND.

It's finished off with a black Swarovski crystal.

This piece is handmade.

A perfect gift for someone special or a bridesmaid.

name: BUTTERFLY necklace - colour choice
description:
Hand-cut acrylic butterfly charm inspired by the enamel painting on a vintage compact. 

Vibrant, striking colour and a one of a kind piece. 

Hangs on a 16 inch chain.

name: Vintage Cameo necklace
description:
Lovely one-of-a-kind cameo necklace.

It's an unusual purple colour in a vintage silver setting.

The charm has been created from a vintage necklace.

name: Horseshoe necklace - sterling silver
description:
Beautiful sterling silver horseshoe necklace.

It's been hand cut to make it unique and hangs on a 16" chain.

name: Black onyx cufflinks
description:
Stunning oval cufflinks set with black onyx stones.

These look great worn with a crisp white shirt for a striking contrast.

name: Heart Hoop earrings
description:
Lovely hoop earrings with hanging heart charms.

A striking look and lightweight feel.

Silver plated.

name: KEY hoop earrings
description:
Cute hoop earrings with hanging key charms.

A striking look and lightweight feel.

Silver plated.

name: WISHBONE necklace
description:
The perfect necklace for Christmas!

A really cute silver look wishbone hanging on a silver plated chain.

A great stocking filler.

name: BLUE RUSSIAN DOLL NECKLACE
description:
Super cute and colourful Russian Doll necklace.

The charms hang on a standard 16" silver plated ball chain.

Great stocking filler!

name: Wee Birdie necklace - rose
description:
Gorgeous little bird charm in a vintage style rose pattern.

Hangs on a silver plated ball chain.

A great stocking filler!

name: GOLD vintage button cuff links
description:
Stunning one-of-a-kind cuff links created from vintage buttons.

They're gold coloured with an oxidised geometric pattern.

Diameter approx. 1.5 cm.

name: YES, I WILL Tiepin
description:
Perfect for the Groom on his big day.

All of our tiepins are made from the pages of old books of Scottish Fairy Tales, making each one unique.

Tiepin is silver plated.

name: LOVE HEART NECKLACE
description:
Hand made silver necklace stamped with the word LOVE.

The silver has been heat treated to give it a lovely texture and make the wording nice and subtle.

It's finished off with a vintage crystal bead making it a truly one of a kind piece.

A perfect gift for someone special or a wedding day necklace for a bride - offering both something old AND something new in one.

name: Wee Birdie necklace - floral
description:
Gorgeous little bird charm in a vintage style orange floral pattern.

Hangs on a silver plated chain.

A great stocking filler!

name: Russian Doll necklaces
description:
Super cute and colourful Russian Doll necklaces.

The charms hang on a standard 16" chain. Silver plated.

Available in Red/Yellow and Purple.

Great stocking fillers!

name: HUSBAND tiepin
description:
Perfect for the Groom on his big day.

All of our tiepins are made from the pages of old books of Scottish Fairy Tales, making each one unique.

Tiepin is silver plated.

name: FATHER tiepin
description:
Perfect for the Father of the Bride or Groom.

All of our tiepins are made from the pages of old books of Scottish Fairy Tales, making each one unique.

Tiepin is silver plated.

name: FAIRY LETTERS
description:
Our Fairy Letters will be back soon - with a brand new design available!

These stunning Fairy Letters each contain a unique "letter" from a book of Scottish fairy tales.

The patterned envelopes hang on 16" (42cm) chains (approx) which come in a choice of copper or silver.

Envelopes measure 2cm x 1cm.

Perfect bridesmaid gifts - can be personalised to your theme.

options.name: COPPER CHAIN - The Gold Grew Dim

name: Get Me To The Church On Time Clock Cufflinks
description:
Unusual clock face cufflinks in a choice of two styles.

These make a great gift for your Best Man and Ushers - and they're a reminder of their duties!

They come in a white vintage look face with a Paris mark or a metal look face.

Cufflinks are silver plated.

name: OVAL FAIRY TALE necklaces
description:
Sweet but striking Fairy Tale necklaces inlaid with text from old books of Scottish Fairy Tales.

These handmade oval charms are one-of-a-kind due to the vintage text.

Ovals are approx 2cm x 1.5cm, the hang on chains of approx 42cm/16"

These necklaces are silver plated

name: Hematite cufflinks
description:
Stunning oval cufflinks set with hematite stones.

These stones are an unusual grey colour with a metallic look.

name: Knights battle cufflinks
description:
One of a kind cufflinks made with text from an old book of Scottish Fairy Tales.

They read "on the castle, where knights battle".

Cufflinks are silver plated.

name: CRYSTAL CHATELAINE NECKLACE
description:
Stunning Chatelaine necklace with four drops all featuring a vintage bead or button.

The chain drops hang from a double circle with a Swarovski crystal bead.

Length of pendant (from top of circle to bottom of longest drop) approx 10cm/4"

Chain length approx 42cm/16"

name: ELFLAND Fairy Tale locket pendant
description:
A one-of-a-kind locket handmade using text from an old book of Scottish Fairy Tales. 

It's a lovely antique gold colour and hangs on a long textured chain.

The book text reads "hillside to Elfland"

name: SWALLOW necklace - colour choice
description:
Hand-cut acrylic swallow charm inspired by the enamel painting on a vintage compact. 

Vibrant, striking colour and a one of a kind piece. 

This little bird is around 3 cms long, and hangs on a silver plated chain measuring 16 inches.

name: CAMEO NECKLACES
description:
Super cute and unusual cameo necklaces with a real vintage feel!

These pictures are set in vintage scallop settings and hang on 18"/42cm copper chains.

Available in black and green.

name: ROUND FAIRY TALE RING - She Was Still Beautiful
description:
Lovely one-of-a-kind Fairy Tale ring.

It's a large round ring inlaid with text from an old book of Scottish Fairy Tales reading "She Was Still Beautiful.

Approx 2cm diameter. Ring is silver plated and size adjustable.

name: Flower cluster rings
description:
Gorgeous little rings featuring clusters of flowers for a vintage feel.

Available in 4 colours they're size adjustable.

Clusters measure approx. 1.8cm

name: Carnation flower rings
description:
Adorable summery flower rings in four different colours.

These striking rings are all size adjustable.

Carnations measure approx. 2.2cm

name: Dahlia flower rings
description:
These super cute, super pretty flower rings are perfect for summer! (Whenever it rocks up.)

They're available in a four colours and are size adjustable.

Flowers measure approx. 2cm

name: VINTAGE BUTTON CUFFLINKS - Green Moon
description:
Introducing the latest addition to our vintage button collection.

Each pair is one-of-a-kind and features a pair of vintage buttons mounted on silver plated cufflinks.

name: Hearts and Flowers cocktail rings
description:
These stunning statement rings give a real pop of colour. Perfect for both nights out and summer days.

They're available in four colours on adjustable silver plated rings.

Hearts measure approx. 3.3 x 3.8cm

name: AMBER PENDANT
description:
Unusual copper coloured pendant featuring a vintage amber-look pendant.

It's complemented by a vintage bead and button, and a key charm.

This pendant is a super-long 30inches (76cm) and is designed to slip over your head (no fastener).

Longest drop measures 3inches (7.5cm).

name: FAIRY TALE BRACELETS - Silver or Gold
description:
The latest addition to the Fairy Tale collection.

These gorgeous bracelets have been made with text from an old book of Scottish fairy tales making each one unique.

name: HEART OF GOLD KILTPIN
description:
A vintage fluted heart charm is the centre piece of this lovely brooch.

It hangs from gold colour chain alongside a vintage pearlised button, and a scroll frame charm.
